description:
The Maestros of the 12. Tango Tage Halle 2015 dance “El Tigre Millán” by Juan D'Arienzo, sung by Alberto Echagüe, in Halle (Saale), Germany.

The Maestros are:
Stephanie Fesneau and Fausto Carpino
Maja Petrović and Marko Miljević
Eleonora Kalganova and Michael Nadtochi
